overview: It has been a long six months of elimination races, but we've finally gotten to the top two mountain bike endurance race teams, Team Skeeter, and Team Slayer. These are the last two teams to battle it out on a three day endurance race that will finally put to rest who is the best, and who will go home with the one hundred thousand dollar prize. Take a ride alongside our teams comprised of luscious females and hunky team captains, as they find love, lust and winning can be a dirty game as they race to the finish line!
title: Mountain High
